to add a new paypal button:

1 after first <form> line paste: 
<div class= "sizedrop">

2 after second <table> line paste: 
</div><div class="addtocartbutton">

3 after the line above closing <form> paste: 
</div>

4 Replace the 'Sizes' text with:
<div class="price">$XX.XX</div>

5 Get rid of both border="0" parts

6 Replace add to cart image ' src="..." ' with: 
class="addtocartbuttonimage" src="img/add-to-cart-button.jpg"

7 change 'method ="post"' in first line to: 
method = "add"